AuroraNow offers an optional premium subscription ("AuroraNow Pro") that unlocks advanced features, custom alert thresholds, and removes advertisements.

Billing: Payment will be charged to your Apple App Store or Google Play account at confirmation of purchase.

Auto-Renewal: Subscriptions automatically renew unless auto-renew is turned off at least 24 hours before the end of the current period.

Management & Cancellation: You can manage or cancel your subscription at any time by going to your App Store or Google Play Account Settings after purchase. Canceling a subscription stops future billing, but no refunds will be provided for the current active period.

